        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Smoke constantly belches from this +1 magic longsword. Any&nbsp;hit with this sword deals 1 extra fire damage. You can use a&nbsp;special action while holding the sword to command the&nbsp;blade’s edges to light on fire.</p>\n<p><strong>Stoke Flames</strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span>&nbsp;(concentrate)</p>\n<p>Until the end of your turn, the blade deals 1d6 extra fire damage instead of just 1. After you use this action, you can’t use it again for 10 minutes.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Automatically applied effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>+1 fire damage, and ability to activate Stoke Flames</li>\n</ul>"
        },
